title: Quality Conversation with Andrew Gough on the God/Quality Question, motorcycles, and much more!!
description: I speak with fellow Zammer about Pirsig, Quality and God...as well as many other topics. Andrew is an Anglican Minister, school chaplain, former philosophy instructor & engineer. He is also an avid motorcyclist and mechanic...and a jazz musician! So you will hear an excellent, multidisciplinary take on our favorite book.
